  <brief_title>The Early Administration of Sodium Thiosulfate Should Help to Reduce the Mortality of Dialysis Patients With Calciphylaxis, From a National Cohort</brief_title>
  <official_title>National Follow-up of Dialysis Patients With Sodium Thiosufate-treated Calciphylaxis Under Temporary Use Authorization</official_title>
